Package: scVeloR
Type: Package
Title: RNA Velocity Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zaoqu", "Liu", 
           email = "liuzaoqu@163.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1234-5678")),
    person("scVelo Team", 
           role = "ctb",
           comment = "Original Python implementation")
    )
Description: A comprehensive R implementation of RNA velocity analysis based on 
    the scvelo Python package. This package enables estimation of RNA velocities 
    for single-cell RNA-seq data, supporting deterministic (steady-state), 
    stochastic, and dynamical models. The dynamical model uses an 
    Expectation-Maximization algorithm to infer full transcriptional kinetics 
    including transcription, splicing, and degradation rates. The package 
    integrates seamlessly with Seurat objects and provides visualization 
    functions for velocity embedding, stream plots, and phase portraits.
